data.description: This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home in Waterford Park is packed with updates! This lovely home features a light and bright open floor plan with a living/dining combo, spacious family room, island kitchen with gas cooking, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and walk-in pantry, first floor primary suite, home office, and well-sized secondary bedrooms. Updates include  a fully bricked outdoor firepit with patio, water softener, tankless water heater, hardwired LAN line Ethernet connection (ideal for gamers!), Cree smart lights on front porch and garage exterior,  upgraded light fixtures in primary suite and laundry room, water heads upgraded in bathrooms, ring doorbell, Kevo smart door lock, storm door with doggy door, and backyard rock landscaping. This home is perfect for entertaining, inside or outside.  You will love the location, it backs to a greenbelt and is nearby neighborhood amenities, schools, shopping and more. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your next home, book your personal tour today!
